serves: 8
---
- 0.25 white cabbage
- 0.25 red cabbage
- 2 carrot
- 1 red pepper
- 50g green onion
- 200g cilantro
- 80g peanut butter
- 0.5 lemon (juice)
- 1.5tbsp rice vinegar
- 1.5tbsp gluten free soy sauce
- 1tbsp date honey
- 1tbsp brown sugar
- 1tbsp sesame oil
- 1tsp sriracha sauce
- 2tsp ginger
- 1 garlic clove
---
Cut vegetables to thin strips.
Make peanut butter dressing: crush/mince garlic and ginger, squeeze the lemon and mix the rest of the ingredients.
Combine everything.







